OL,3,CWill the Spring Statement bring
OL,4,Csqueezed living standards and gloomy
OL,5,Cforecasts?
OL,7,FI have a few more reflections to share
OL,8,Fon Chancellor Rachel Reeves' Spring
OL,9,FStatement that we'll hear on Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe first is that the Office for
OL,12,FBudget Responsibility is bound to make
OL,13,Fa gloomier forecast for real household
OL,14,Fdisposable income - a proxy for our
OL,15,Fliving standards - than even the
OL,16,Fpretty gloomy forecast it made in
OL,17,FOctober.
