OL,3,CWill the Spring Statement bring
OL,4,Csqueezed living standards and gloomy
OL,5,Cforecasts?
OL,7,FBack then, it said Real Household
OL,8,FDisposable Income (RHDI) would rise in
OL,9,Fthis parliament a paltry 0.5% a year
OL,10,Fon average.
OL,12,FSneeze and any rise in our living
OL,13,Fstandards would vanish.
OL,15,FThere's been a sneezing fit.
OL,17,FWell, as I reported last week, it is
OL,18,Fdowngrading this year's GDP growth
OL,19,Fforecast from 2% to 1%, and will also
OL,20,Fcut its forecast for next year from
OL,21,F1.8%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
