OL,3,CWill the Spring Statement bring
OL,4,Csqueezed living standards and gloomy
OL,5,Cforecasts?
OL,7,FBut perhaps most significant of all,
OL,8,Fthe government's choice to reduce
OL,9,Fpayments to the disabled and
OL,10,Fincapacitated by #6 billion a year
OL,11,Fwill significantly reduce the living
OL,12,Fstandards of the losers and bring down
OL,13,Fthe average rise in RHDI.
OL,15,FI wouldn't be at all surprised if the
OL,16,Fforecast increases in living standards
OL,17,Fhave been wiped out completely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
