OL,3,CWill the Spring Statement bring
OL,4,Csqueezed living standards and gloomy
OL,5,Cforecasts?
OL,7,FWhich is bad news for all of us, and
OL,8,Fterrible political news for Prime
OL,9,FMinister Keir Starmer - because it was
OL,10,Fonly a few weeks ago that he said his
OL,11,Ftop priority for the parliament was to
OL,12,Fincrease RHDI in every region of the
OL,13,FUK.
OL,15,FSo when the OBR announces the
OL,16,Fdisappointing prediction, you can bet
OL,17,Fthe falling value of your house that
OL,18,FStarmer will say he is minded to go
OL,19,F"further and faster" to reform the
OL,20,Feconomy and revive living standards -
OL,21,Fand will cross fingers and toes.
