OL,3,CWill the Spring Statement bring
OL,4,Csqueezed living standards and gloomy
OL,5,Cforecasts?
OL,7,FI have two other facts to share.
OL,9,FThe first is that Reeves will only
OL,10,Fmake spending and welfare cuts that
OL,11,Frestore her eroded fiscal headroom of
OL,12,Fa short #9.9 billion, rather than
OL,13,Fincrease it.
OL,15,FThis is a pretty racy bet by her.
OL,16,FShe's taking a big economic and
OL,17,Fpolitical risk in not increasing
OL,18,Fheadroom to double or treble that.
OL,20,FThe point is that #9.9 billion is
OL,21,Falmost no buffer or headroom at all.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
