OL,3,CWill the Spring Statement bring
OL,4,Csqueezed living standards and gloomy
OL,5,Cforecasts?
OL,7,FFinally here is a treat for the fiscal
OL,8,Fgeeks.
OL,10,FReeves has had a lucky fiscal windfall
OL,11,Ffrom the decision to fund the pledged
OL,12,F#6 billion a year rise in defence
OL,13,Fspending with a #6 billion cut in
OL,14,Foverseas aid.
OL,16,FWell, the development budget is
OL,17,Fresource (RDEL) whereas most of
OL,18,Fdefence is capital (CDEL).
OL,20,FNow please don't deafen me with your
OL,21,Fcries of "you what?!!!!!" I'll explain.
